### 7. CUSTOM SCENARIO RULES
• In Age 2 and three there will be two races. Human barbarians in the highlands of the north and a race of aberrations with powerful magic will rule the south.
• The two races are in a state of war for the entire time. Diplomacy actions are disabled
• Aberration race civilization naturally growth for tech (magic) is double (+40% per round)
• Aberration race prefers the south and will only settle in regions 6 and 7 (preferring 7)
• Barbarian race civilization growth for military is double (+40% per round)
• Barbarian race will only settle in regions 2 and 3 preferring 3
• Diving shaping actions that increase tech (magic) for the aberration civilization give an extra +1 tech +1 military from their magical talent
• Shaping actions that increase barbarian settlement size give an extra +1
• Age 3 will end with a cataclysm that brings an end to the aberration's empire leaving the humans to begin age 4 on their own
 

